flowchart TD
    Start([User Opens Register Page]) --> InputData[User Enters:<br/>- Username<br/>- Email<br/>- Password<br/>- Confirm Password]
    
    InputData --> SubmitForm[User Clicks Register Button]
    
    SubmitForm --> ValidateClient{Client-Side<br/>Validation}
    
    ValidateClient -->|Invalid| ShowClientError[Display Error Message:<br/>- Empty fields<br/>- Invalid email format<br/>- Password mismatch<br/>- Weak password]
    ShowClientError --> InputData
    
    ValidateClient -->|Valid| SendRequest[Send POST Request<br/>to /api/register]
    
    SendRequest --> ValidateServer{Server-Side<br/>Validation}
    
    ValidateServer -->|Invalid Data| ReturnError400[Return 400:<br/>Validation Error]
    ReturnError400 --> DisplayError[Display Error Message]
    DisplayError --> InputData
    
    ValidateServer -->|Valid| CheckExists{Username/Email<br/>Already Exists?}
    
    CheckExists -->|Yes| ReturnError409[Return 409:<br/>Conflict Error]
    ReturnError409 --> DisplayConflict[Display:<br/>'User already exists']
    DisplayConflict --> InputData
    
    CheckExists -->|No| HashPassword[Hash Password<br/>using bcrypt/Argon2]
    
    HashPassword --> SaveDB[Save User to Database:<br/>- username<br/>- email<br/>- password_hash<br/>- created_at]
    
    SaveDB --> DBSuccess{Database<br/>Operation<br/>Successful?}
    
    DBSuccess -->|No| ReturnError500[Return 500:<br/>Server Error]
    ReturnError500 --> DisplayServerError[Display:<br/>'Registration failed.<br/>Try again']
    DisplayServerError --> InputData
    
    DBSuccess -->|Yes| GenerateToken[Generate JWT Token/<br/>Session ID]
    
    GenerateToken --> ReturnSuccess[Return 201:<br/>Registration Successful<br/>+ Auth Token]
    
    ReturnSuccess --> StoreToken[Store Token in:<br/>- LocalStorage/SessionStorage<br/>- Cookie]
    
    StoreToken --> RedirectDashboard[Redirect to<br/>Dashboard/Login Page]
    
    RedirectDashboard --> End([Registration Complete])
    
    style Start fill:#90EE90
    style End fill:#FFB6C6
    style ShowClientError fill:#FFE4B5
    style DisplayError fill:#FFE4B5
    style DisplayConflict fill:#FFE4B5
    style DisplayServerError fill:#FFE4B5
    style SaveDB fill:#87CEEB
    style HashPassword fill:#DDA0DD
    style GenerateToken fill:#DDA0DD
    style RedirectDashboard fill:#98FB98
